{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 1503241, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Greenhooves", "body": "Frankly, I'm a bit peeved that you only kill him on Heroic. It sets a bad precedent.\n\nSuppose they did this all the major bosses. No LK kill, no Yogg kill, no Illidan, Kael-Thas, or Gruul unless you do Heroic.", "date": "2011-08-25T14:11:16-05:00", "rating": 14, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Gruul, and he was a pansy.", "creationdate": "2013-08-18T20:25:59-05:00", "id": 685802, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1503241, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GreySage", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-03-09T16:54:48-06:00", 1, "Greenhooves"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 21, "id": 1512123, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ravencrofts", "body": "Mortal Insects! You dare tresspass into MY domain? Your arrogance will be purged in living flame.\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_AGGRO.ogg')[/quote]\n\nNot ... No! That should be my finest hour! [i](?)[/i]\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_DEATH_HEROIC.ogg')[/quote]\n\nToo soon! ... You have come too soon...\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_DEATH_NORMAL.ogg')[/quote]\n\nYou will be destroyed! [i](?)[/i]\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HAMMER_DROP_01.ogg')[/quote]\n\nDie!\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HAMMER_DROP_02.ogg')[/quote]\n\nYour judgement has come!\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HAMMER_DROP_03.ogg')[/quote]\n\nEnough! I will finish this.\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HAMMER_PICKUP_01.ogg')[/quote]\n\nFall to your knees, mortals! This ends now.\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HAMMER_PICKUP_02.ogg')[/quote]\n\nSulfuras will be your end.\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HAMMER_PICKUP_03.ogg')[/quote]\n\nThe realm of fire will consume you!\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_PURGE_01.ogg')[/quote]\n\nDie, insect!\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_KILL_01.ogg')[/quote]\n\nPathetic.\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_KILL_02.ogg')[/quote]\n\nThis is MY realm!\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_KILL_03.ogg')[/quote]\n\nAll ... EVERYTHING! [i](?)[/i]\n[quote]/script PlaySoundFile('sound/CREATURE/RAGNAROS/VO_FL_RAGNAROS_HEROIC_FIGHT_01.ogg')[/quote]\n\nAh, intruder! This realm is not your