{"commentv2": 1, "number": 58, "id": 2014853, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "benx2011", "body": "As in 6.02, I just solo it as a 562 Firemage. It only took me around 30 seconds to kill it. Just cast Time Ward, Living Bomb, Mirror Image then nuke him down. If you have high DPS, you can drain his Hp down to 30% before he throws the hammer. Once he throws the hammer onto the ground, you can either kill the fire elementals before they reach to the hammer, or just pop Ice Block until Raggy comes out again and nuke him down. He will probably then throw the hammer again before he dies. Each firenova from the fire elemental deals around 4.5K damage, with your Frost shield, you should be able to take all the damage without dying. As a 562 mage, i have 88K HP. so just kill the 2 fire elementals that attack you. when Raggy comes out again, just kill it.", "date": "2014-10-17T21:43:50-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2014-10-17T21:46:56-05:00", 2, "benx2011"]}
