{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 118691, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Vala", "body": "Also drops the rare Eye of Sulfuras, a key part in creating Sulfuras, Hand of Ragnaros. Drop rate seems to around 1-3%.\r\nHad 1 drop in about 30 kills.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.wowhead.com/?item=17204#00z", "date": "2007-07-10T17:04:16-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
