{"commentv2": 1, "number": 22, "id": 192680, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "98388", "body": "I may never get to experience this guy, so this joke has gone over my head many times.\r\nWhat's the deal with telling people you can look through a window to see him?  what happens when you do that?", "date": "2007-11-28T09:10:56-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I've never been in MC either, but I believe this is it: There's a  fiery crack in the rock behind some boss. If you go stand in it, you take lots of damage and soon die. Some people try to trick newbies by telling that you can actually see Ragnaros by going close enough and changing your camera angle in some way.  I suppose humans are a bit sadistic by nature...", "creationdate": "2007-11-28T09:47:30-06:00", "id": 19790, "rating": 51, "commentid": 192680, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "hezec", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Its behind Golemagg.", "creationdate": "2008-11-29T08:40:23-06:00", "id": 60299, "rating": 33, "commentid": 192680, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arovei", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Ahh the good memories of gearing up newbies in my old guild...  Particularly loved the time when someone died there during the fight and 6 people STILL went to \"look at rag.\"", "creationdate": "2009-03-02T19:27:57-06:00", "id": 83391, "rating": 24, "commentid": 192680, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "cheesechamp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I will tell u dat [b]no actual graphycs were harmed during the making of Molten Core[/b], Hezec :)", "creationdate": "2009-0