{"commentv2": 1, "number": 46, "id": 620491, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Copybass", "body": "I used [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=44228]Baby Spice[/url] on him. It's very fun to see Ragnaros become not but a tiny boss. My raid laughed quite hard, seeing him shrink, though, I would not suggest it. Our raid leader got a little ticked, as Ragnaros becomes hard to hit if you shrink him. He is too far into the middle of the lava, and getting close for hitting him causes you damage. It still looks hillarious though.", "date": "2009-02-23T11:21:08-06:00", "rating": 40, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "And Lil' Ragnaros was born.", "creationdate": "2013-04-05T23:18:11-05:00", "id": 648759, "rating": 7, "commentid": 620491, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "DatRandomGuy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "ROLFMAO dude thats awesome", "creationdate": "2013-07-01T16:19:47-05:00", "id": 674006, "rating": 1, "commentid": 620491, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Delerio1", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 47, "id": 621099, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Artharas", "body": "Just soloed him and the rest of MC as a prot paladin. [url=http://img100.imageshack.us/img100/8655/raggysolo.jpg]Pic[/url].\n\nLike you saw it took ~70 minutes getting the kill, my weapon broke at ~60% which made the fight a lot harder(less SoW/JoL proccs). So bring another 1-2 weapons for a lot easier and faster kill.\n\nI had 413 FR with FR aura and used SoW/JoL and Sacred up constantly. I was hoping I would be able to jump out of Wrath of Ragnaros's knockback range every ~25sec, but my initial feeling was right, he doesn't use it unless someone is in melee range. This made the fight a lot more trickier.\n\nI placed myself [url=http://img100.imageshack.us/img100/8962/placement.jpg]here[/url] so I would always get thrown in the lava and therefor avoid the fall damage. It is very important to stay close to the inner circle's lava, since the room for where you hit the floor in the lava is somewhat limited(and ofcourse lag here = baaaad if anyone remembers the lava jump in BRM :P).\nI recommend saving Divine Shield for when you get both Hand of Ragnaros and Wrath of Ragnaros at the same time, I f.x. died once from getting shot out of melee range from Hand of Ragnaros and then when I was running back into my position I got Wrath of Ragnaros'd and didn't land in lava(since I wasn't yet near the inner circle lava). I used JoL/ShoR/HotR every 9s(waiting for J instead of doing 6s abilities first).\n\nWhen the Sons come, go to 969 rotation but depending on mana you might want to skip consecrate. Your goal is to keep 1-2 adds alive and be at full mana ASAP. Then you heal up to full health and kill the remaining adds and rinse and repeat.\n\nNote: You can also FoL between his swings if you're lacking health in between Son Phases.\n\nIn the end was merely done to prove I could and due to lack of challenges :)", "date": "2009-02-23T21:26:48-06:00", "rating": 31, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-02-24T02:53:13-06:00", 1, "Artharas"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 629956, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "103638", "body": "i sawl this guy in a video called \" The Grind \" Halloween special its hilareous! you'll see him sommoning mr. teeth, well i do not know why his name is mr. teath but you'll here him saying \" why hello how are u today there... [Rawr] go to youtube and watch youll see him in the middle of the video i bet u would see the ppl who watch this!", "date": "2009-03-03T13:20:25-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-03-03T13:20:47-06:00", 1, "103638"]}
