{"commentv2": 1, "number": 61, "id": 767937, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "llubtoille", "body": "Solo'd as a ret pally\n395 fire resist, basically the lev 70 badge FR gear + blacksmithing FR helm + FR aura.\nonly hard part's making sure you land in the lava after the punts.\ndamage is minimal, SS + JoL + SoL keeps you at full most of the time.\ntook about 4 waves of sons, so I'd guess 25mins.\n\nhttp://i138.photobucket.com/albums/q278/N_Crawler/RagSolod1.jpg\nhttp://i138.photobucket.com/albums/q278/N_Crawler/Ragsolod2.jpg\n\n- didn't take any screens mid fight, as it stalls my computer for a few secs >.<\n\nwiped the first time, got him to 10% but 3 bad punts in a row gibbed me.\n(bubbled after first, LoH after 2nd, hadn't learned my lesson by the 3rd)\n\nnot something I'd care to do again.", "date": "2009-07-04T19:50:12-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Id ask sth ... is he actually soloable as a 80 PvE and DPS gear with bout 2-3 good weps ? And is it  true dat ur http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=49909( DK Icy Touch ) will do [b]A LOT[/b] of DMG on him and his sons ? Weps are Sword of Justice ( http://www.wowhead.com/?item=37653 ),  Claymore of the Prophet ( http://www.wowhead.com/?item=45074 ) and 2 lovely Reapers of Dark Souls, got with rep from the Ebon Blade quartermaster ( http://www.wowhead.com/?item=44250 ).", "creationdate": "2009-07-25T08:53:22-05:00", "id": 417149, "rating": 0, "commentid": 767937, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "depevlad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-07-04T19:51:16-05:00", 1, "llubtoille"]}
