{"commentv2": 1, "number": 67, "id": 812859, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Garltok", "body": "Would this guy be harder, easier or about the same toughness to kill as onyxia? I have solo'd Onyxia on my lvl 80 Blood death knight.", "date": "2009-08-15T20:49:43-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I don't know why this comment was downrated, it's an honest question.  Due to mechanics, anyone without a charge mechanism will find this tougher than ony, since Rag blasts anyone not in his melee. He also hits about the same as Ony used to, so yeah, he's tougher than old ony.", "creationdate": "2009-10-22T05:59:27-05:00", "id": 128621, "rating": 4, "commentid": 812859, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "467494", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
