{"commentv2": 1, "number": 157, "id": 1449954, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "menacebysociety", "body": "This was easily done solo by me, an ilvl 339 prot pally.  I did die the first try from the knockback, but kind of gauged where I'd need to be to hit lava instead on my 2nd try.  It's pretty much a tank and spank, just keep your resistance aura up, and upon landing from knockback (in lava, of course), head right back up and spank repeatedly :).  Sons are no biggie, they fall easily to HotR/Cons/AS.\r\n\r\nI had tried an earlier poster's recommended spot to melee, and it was a difficult spot to master, hence the death on the first try.  Here is where I stood to melee, and fell safely in lava :P\r\n\r\nhttp://i1100.photobucket.com/albums/g410/menacebysociety/Rag1.jpg\r\n\r\nGood luck!", "date": "2011-06-25T00:55:07-05:00", "rating": 19, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thank you thank you thank you!  I tried the previous location too and just died.  I tried yours and it was perfect!  And I got my Judgement Legplates, WOOT!", "creationdate": "2011-11-12T13:34:07-06:00", "id": 277328, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1449954, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Crystallyne", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That was the perfect spot. Thank you so much for that.", "creationdate": "2011-12-11T12:27:18-06:00", "id": 495743, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1449954, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "229034", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I died several times as a pally trying to do this, I had a very difficult time finding that \"sweet\" spot. This picture was the perfect thing for me. I zoomed in a bit on the minimap and got right into position. If I turned my camera angle around I could clearly see I would miss the rock formation. This is frustrating, I guess I hadn't tried to solo this as a melee character, just a hunter with a pet. Thanks for the picture, it was v v helpful!", "creationdate": "2012-05-01T00:35:12-05:00", "id": 540080, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1449954, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "texanwmn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Rag is pretty easily soloed as a holy pally. Denounce is your friend here and holy shock used as damage will actually kill him pretty fast. just make sure to stand back a bit on the 2nd row of stone and you wont have to worry about the knock back too much.", "creationdate": "2013-08-07T02:15:20-05:00", "id": 683149, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1449954, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "1136878", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
