{"commentv2": 1, "number": 191, "id": 1752376, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Lomedae", "body": "As a follow up to the 4.x solo reports for anyone that's curious.\r\nAt level 90 it's as trivial a fight as you would expect, allowing you to ignore all mechanics. \r\nAs a heroic geared Balance specced Druid the fight lasted 35 seconds, with him doing only 51k damage in total.", "date": "2012-10-28T06:52:09-05:00", "rating": 12, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "do you think a 90 rogue would have any trouble?", "creationdate": "2012-11-02T19:32:49-05:00", "id": 594477, "rating": -3, "commentid": 1752376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "883211", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Like he said, it's a trivial fight. At level 90, any class should beat him before his second phase.", "creationdate": "2012-12-09T11:40:42-06:00", "id": 609725, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1752376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "1029787", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "At level 90 the dialogue lasts longer than the fight.", "creationdate": "2013-05-02T13:45:33-05:00", "id": 655695, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1752376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "voodoopimp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "to seanlb: I was able to solo him with a Subtelty-spec Rogue at level 85, using a mix of quest blues and Pandarian greens. You should have no trouble at 90.", "creationdate": "2013-06-11T06:21:12-05:00", "id": 667983, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1752376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Aussiegnome8", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He was being solo'd as early as WotLK.", "creationdate": "2013-10-13T11:10:51-05:00", "id": 700892, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1752376, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ceasure", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
