{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 1911610, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Lucidic", "body": "In the celestial tournament I was having a hard time with [url=npc=71930]Shademaster Kiryn[/url] because of [url=npc=72097]Stormoen[/url] and [url=npc=71933]Blingtron 4000[/url] because of [url=npc=72100]Lil' B[/url] until I used this guy.  For both enemies just [url=petability=503]Flamethrower[/url] and [url=petability=179]Conflagrate[/url] then they are dead.  Since the bonus damage from [url=petability=179]Conflagrate[/url] is a separate hit, the first nuke kills the mechanical and the second hit kills them again, negating their free one time rez.  This guy is just CRAZY good against mechanicals.  Don't forget to [url=petability=319]Magma Wave[/url] after [url=npc=72097]Stormoen[/url] is dead to clean up that turret.", "date": "2013-10-24T08:14:50-05:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-10-24T08:16:46-05:00", 1, "Lucidic"]}
