{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 753961, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "AzurePai", "body": "When completing [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=11966]this Horde quest[/url] or [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=11964]this Alliance quest[/url], the summer Scorchling will do the following:\r\n\r\n[quote]Festival Scorchling says: Thank you again, <name>, for this delectable incense.\r\nFestival Scorchling devours the incense. It's ravenous!\r\nFestival Scorchling says: So good! So packed with energy!\r\nFestival Scorchling says: It has everything a growing scorchling needs!\r\nFestival Scorchling says: I can feel the power SURGING within me!\r\nFestival Scorchling bellows with laughter!\r\nFestival Scorchling says: Now! Finally! Our plans can take effect!\r\nFestival Scorchling says: KNEEL, LITTLE MORTAL! KNEEL BEFORE THE MIGHT OF THE HERALD OF RAGNAROS!\r\nFestival Scorchling says: YOU WILL ALL PERISH IN FLAMES!\r\nFestival Scorchling blinks...\r\nFestival Scorchling says: Ah. I was merely jesting...[/quote]It will continue to grow until the lines in all caps, when the wisp appears. It's huge, but nowhere as big as the real Ragnaros, and the scorchling will then immediately shrink back to its original size and says it's joking.\r\n\r\nOr is it....?", "date": "2009-06-21T16:14:39-05:00", "rating": 19, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Now we have cataclysm......", "creationdate": "2009-10-01T13:57:34-05:00", "id": 125369, "rating": 11, "commentid": 753961, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "330050", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
