{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 1101980, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "isride", "body": "23.4 million.  But you get some mega buffs to help you, on my shammy my lightning bolts were hitting for 100k+ and my flame shock was ticking for around 20k.  It's difficult to give exact numbers though because the current beta phase doesn't have working combat text for the damage you do.", "date": "2010-08-16T17:34:59-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Mega buffs against Ragnaros or against Deathwing?", "creationdate": "2010-09-04T19:03:29-05:00", "id": 457927, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1101980, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lurtzello", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "As far as i know, when Malfurion and Hamuul are casting thier beams /spells he takes a big increase in damage. Iv seen him take up to 317,000 from a shadowbolt.  Example below. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGODVleq-h4&feature=related", "creationdate": "2010-09-12T02:20:18-05:00", "id": 181606, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1101980, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kyzen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
