{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 1215018, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "totorz", "body": "When Malfurion has no mobs on him he channels [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=76232]Storm's Fury[/url].\nFor Hamuul, it's [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=95724]Earth's Rage[/url].\n\nIf you are soloing this, you only really need to help out the one that increases your damage, since neither can die.\n\nThe event is like [url=http://www.wowhead.com/quest=13267/the-battle-for-the-undercity]The Battle For The Undercity[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/quest=25393]Operation: Gnomeregan[/url] or [url=http://www.wowhead.com/quest=25445]Zalazane's Fall[/url] in that the first person in the area triggers a countdown( in this case 2 minutes after talking to Cenarius), with everyone who comes in after the end of the countdown having to wait until the current event is finished to watch the start of the next event. The difference here though is that the quest to defeat Ragnaros is given outside, not at the start of the event, so joining in midway through the fight  only means you missed some roleplay.\n\nOh yeah, and a heads up to shadow priests; Do not use Shadow Word: Death.", "date": "2010-12-08T13:17:14-06:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "All Shadow Priests who USED Shadow Word: Death here, raise your hand!  .o/", "creationdate": "2011-01-01T13:11:59-06:00", "id": 210647, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1215018, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Znuff", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-12-09T06:35:01-06:00", 3, "totorz"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 8, "id": 1283460, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "748840", "body": "What does Shadow Word: Death do, why not use it? T_T", "date": "2011-01-08T05:03:19-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "if you don't kill your target with it you take 50% of the damage you deal yourself. (and with the 4000% damage it would hurt)", "creationdate": "2011-01-12T07:49:19-06:00", "id": 214509, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1283460, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Laurathos", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
